  <series>MU3E_FPGA_IP</series>
  <version>1.0.0</version>
  <description>CMSIS-SVD description of the generic 256-word scratchpad RAM slave window used by Mu3e FEB control paths. BaseAddress is 0 because this file describes the relative window; system integration supplies the live slave base address.</description>
